    "Management": {
      "text": "Warm compresses\nNSAIDs\nBased on etiology\nBacterial -\ncephalexin\n500mg q6 until culture results\nAdd\nTMP-SMX\n(TMP 160mg q12hr) if concern for MRSA\nProtozoal or fungal - treat underlying infection\nSystemic, inflammatory/noninfectious - investigate underlying etiology",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
